@solemage2 wrote:

Im in same boat lol I lagged when I was done pking, walking out with no one around, lagged and ended up in lummy:p
lost wip full rune berserker,glory,obbecape, and the rest of my goodies. All i have left is about 50k and d med…

Tips:

If you have good stats try staking a bit…“boxing”
stake 5k at first till you know you can beat the guy, then start staking more. if you start to lose stop…

you can merchan d longs, I used to do that, some people sell d longs for 85-90k get 1 and sell for 95-100 and keep doign for a while…

Hope that helps ya
